column1: query

SELECT age, age FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND age IN (SELECT age FROM PilotSkills AS q WHERE  q.age < 53 LIMIT 8) ORDER BY age ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT pilot_name), COUNT(DISTINCT age) FROM PilotSkills WHERE  age > 8
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PilotSkills.plane_name) FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE PilotSkills.age > 30;
SELECT MAX(age), COUNT(DISTINCT age) FROM PilotSkills WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10;
SELECT SUM(age), age FROM PilotSkills WHERE plane_name NOT IN (SELECT plane_name FROM Hangar LIMIT 10) ORDER BY age DESC LIMIT 3
SELECT age, plane_name FROM PilotSkills WHERE  age <= 14 LIMIT 9
SELECT age, location FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR plane_name < (SELECT MAX(plane_name) FROM PilotSkills AS y)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT age), COUNT(DISTINCT pilot_name), age FROM PilotSkills WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  age != 69 ORDER BY age ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT location) FROM Hangar WHERE location IN (SELECT location FROM Hangar AS s LIMIT 9) LIMIT 10
SELECT plane_name, AVG(age) AS average_age FROM PilotSkills GROUP BY plane_name HAVING AVG(age) <= 23 ORDER BY plane_name ASC;
SELECT age FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE age > 10;
SELECT t.age, t.pilot_name FROM PilotSkills JOIN PilotSkills AS t ON PilotSkills.pilot_name = t.pilot_name WHERE  PilotSkills.age >= 53 ORDER BY t.pilot_name ASC LIMIT 2

SELECT PilotSkills.plane_name, Hangar.plane_name, location FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR age = 57 GROUP BY PilotSkills.plane_name ORDER BY PilotSkills.plane_name DESC;
SELECT age FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  age > 28 ORDER BY age DESC
SELECT age, age FROM PilotSkills WHERE  age > 80 ORDER BY age ASC
SELECT v.age FROM PilotSkills AS v WHERE v.age >= 58 GROUP BY v.age LIMIT 7
SELECT age FROM PilotSkills WHERE age > 81 ORDER BY age DESC LIMIT 3

SELECT PilotSkills.age, PilotSkills.plane_name FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM PilotSkills AS T1 WHERE T1.age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND T1.plane_name = PilotSkills.plane_name) GROUP BY PilotSkills.plane_name ORDER BY PilotSkills.age DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT MAX(age) FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE  age <= 80

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Hangar.plane_name), PilotSkills.pilot_name FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE PilotSkills.age IN (SELECT age FROM PilotSkills GROUP BY age HAVING COUNT(age) > 1) GROUP BY PilotSkills.pilot_name ORDER BY PilotSkills.pilot_name DESC
SELECT MAX(PS.age), PS.age FROM PilotSkills AS h JOIN PilotSkills AS PS ON PS.pilot_name = h.pilot_name WHERE pilot_name >= (SELECT MAX(pilot_name) FROM PilotSkills WHERE  age <= 65 LIMIT 4)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT plane_name), plane_name FROM PilotSkills WHERE  age < 60 GROUP BY plane_name HAVING COUNT(age) = 15

SELECT pilot_name, pilot_name FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Hangar AS H WHERE PilotSkills.pilot_name = H.plane_name)
SELECT w.age FROM PilotSkills AS w WHERE  w.age <= 10 ORDER BY w.age DESC LIMIT 4

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT age), age, Hangar.plane_name FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM PilotSkills WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Hangar.plane_name = plane_name)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT age), PilotSkills.plane_name FROM PilotSkills JOIN Hangar ON PilotSkills.plane_name = Hangar.plane_name WHERE age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  age <= 19 ORDER BY PilotSkills.plane_name DESC
